59
00:04:15,330 --> 00:04:17,900
Maybe we should stay at your place tonight.

60
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:19,960
Has the fire damage been repaired yet?

61
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,430
The insurance company is still dicking me around.

62
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:23,600
Won't give me a check.

63
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:25,300
Don't worry about it. I'll be moving out soon.

64
00:04:25,330 --> 00:04:27,730
Stop leeching off your brother? Whatever for?

65
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:30,030
