It's the dragon zombie.

70
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:49,100
Cody likes to hide things in my bag.

71
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:51,030
He's trying to control you.

72
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:52,860
By hiding toys in your bag,

73
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:55,930
you have no choice but to return them to him.

74
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:58,530
He's 7. He seldom has thoughts more complicated

75
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,960
than the desire for candy.

76
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,260
I'll see you at your loft tonight.

77
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:10,430
Oh,honey -- honey,no.

78
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,660
No.

79
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,960
You said we could make breakfast.

80
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,960
