00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:26,700
Nothing you could do,Dexter,would scare me.

544
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:32,000
I believe you.

545
00:29:34,530 --> 00:29:36,000
Come here.

546
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:42,260
