564
00:30:53,760 --> 00:30:55,460
Why?

565
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:57,860
They don't like each other anymore.

566
00:30:57,900 --> 00:30:59,960
Well,that's not true.

567
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:05,800
Does that mean he doesn't like us,either?

568
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:10,200
Oh,no. Of course he likes you.

569
00:31:10,230 --> 00:31:15,760
It's just...It's hard when two people break up.

570
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:19,400
It makes them sad to see each other.

571
00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:21,900
I don't think Dexter's gonna be coming for breakfast

572
