578
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,830
I open myself up for attack or capture

579
00:31:40,860 --> 00:31:44,030
I need to embrace who I am, who I have always been.

580
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:47,060
I need to kill the man who murdered my mother.

581
00:31:52,100 --> 00:31:55,730
I'd almost forgotten this feeling --

582
00:31:55,760 --> 00:32:00,830
driving toward a kill,all my senses sharpened.

583
00:32:00,860 --> 00:32:03,500
It's like I have been living underwater,

584
00:32:03,530 --> 00:32:06,800
holding my breath,and now I can finally breathe.

585
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:11,500
So how come it's so suffocating in here?

586
00:32:18,930 --> 00:32:20,800
James.

587
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:24,530
Hey. It's nice to see you.

588
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:27,900
