595
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:44,860
You can meet him tonight. 9:00,Bar at the hilton.

596
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:46,360
I'll be there.

597
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:57,330
Sergeant doakes. I appreciate your time.

