607
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:24,260
The rodrigo case -- lost due to bad bloodwork.

608
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:26,760
Excuse me?

609
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:30,100
Oh,you weren't aware of that?

610
00:33:30,130 --> 00:33:31,730
The d.A. Didn't get a conviction.

611
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:33,430
That's all I know.

612
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:38,200
Are we through here,sir?

613
00:33:38,230 --> 00:33:41,460
No,actually. We're just getting -- we're done.

614
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:52,800
